$tharaa-transition-base: 250ms ease;
$tharaa-transition-slow: 400ms ease;
```

#### **Ù…Ø«Ø§Ù„ ØªØ·Ø¨ÙŠÙ‚ÙŠ - Button Component:**

```scss
// ğŸ“ src/assets/styles/03-components/_buttons.scss

// ===================================
// Tharaa Buttons
// ===================================

.tharaa-btn {
  // Base styles (Ù…ØªÙˆØ§ÙÙ‚Ø© Ù…Ø¹ Ø³Ù„Ø©)
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: $tharaa-space-3 $tharaa-space-6;
  font-family: $tharaa-font-primary;
  font-size: $tharaa-text-base;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.5;
  text-align: center;
  border: 2px solid transparent;
  border-radius: $tharaa-radius-md;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all $tharaa-transition-base;
  
  // Luxury touch
  letter-spacing: 0.025em;
  
  // Icon support
  &__icon {
    margin-inline-end: $tharaa-space-2;
    font-size: 1.125em;
  }
  
  // ===================================
  // Modifiers
  // ===================================
  
  // Primary Luxury
  &--luxury {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, $tharaa-color-primary 0%, #2a2a2a 100%);
    color: $tharaa-color-secondary;
    border-color: $tharaa-color-secondary;
    box-shadow: $tharaa-shadow-md;
    
    &:hover {
      background: $tharaa-color-secondary;
      color: $tharaa-color-primary;
      box-shadow: $tharaa-shadow-lg;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
  }
  
  // Outline style
  &--outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: $tharaa-color-primary;
    border-color: currentColor;
    
    &:hover {
      background: $tharaa-color-primary;
      color: white;
    }
  }
  
  // Gold accent
  &--gold {
    background: $tharaa-color-secondary;
    color: $tharaa-color-primary;
    
    &:hover {
      background: darken($tharaa-color-secondary, 10%);
      box-shadow: $tharaa-shadow-lg;
    }
  }
  
  // ===================================
  // States
  // ===================================
  
  &.is-loading {
    position: relative;
    color: transparent;
    pointer-events: none;
    
    &::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      border: 2px solid currentColor;
      border-right-color: transparent;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: spin 0.6s linear infinite;
    }
  }
  
  &:disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
}

@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}
```

### ğŸ¨ 2. Ø¨Ù†ÙŠØ© Sections & Blocks

#### **Ø§Ù„ÙØ±Ù‚ Ø¨ÙŠÙ† Sections Ùˆ Components:**

| Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙÙ‡ÙˆÙ… | Ø§Ù„Ø§Ø³ØªØ®Ø¯Ø§Ù… | Ø§Ù„Ù…ÙˆÙ‚Ø¹ | Ù…Ø«Ø§Ù„ |
|---------|-----------|---------|------|
| **Section** | ÙƒØªÙ„ ÙƒØ¨ÙŠØ±Ø© Ù…Ù† Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø­ØªÙˆÙ‰ | Ø¯Ø§Ø®Ù„ Ø§Ù„ØµÙØ­Ø§Øª | Hero, Products Grid, Testimonials |
| **Component** | Ø¹Ù†Ø§ØµØ± Ù‚Ø§Ø¨Ù„Ø© Ù„Ø¥Ø¹Ø§Ø¯Ø© Ø§Ù„Ø§Ø³ØªØ®Ø¯Ø§Ù… | ÙÙŠ Ø£ÙŠ Ù…ÙƒØ§Ù† | Button, Card, Modal |
| **Block** | ÙˆØ­Ø¯Ø© Ù…Ù† Twig | twilight.json | `{% block content %}` |

#### **Ù…Ø«Ø§Ù„ Ø¹Ù…Ù„ÙŠ - Home Page Architecture:**

```twig
