## 4ï¸âƒ£ Ù‡ÙˆÙŠØ© Ø«ÙŠÙ… Tharaa (Tharaa Theme Identity)

### ğŸ¨ Design Tokens Ø§Ù„ÙƒØ§Ù…Ù„Ø©

```scss
// ğŸ“ src/assets/styles/00-settings/_tharaa-tokens.scss

// ===================================
// THARAA IDENTITY SYSTEM
// ===================================

// Brand Colors
$tharaa-colors: (
  // Primary Palette - Dark Luxury
  'charcoal': #1a1a1a,
  'charcoal-light': #2c2c2c,
  'charcoal-dark': #0f0f0f,
  
  // Accent Palette - Gold
  'gold': #d4af37,
