# Ã°Å¸â€œÅ¡ Tharaa Theme - Complete Development Reference Manual
### Comprehensive Guide for Building Professional Salla Themes

**Version:** 2.0  
**Last Updated:** February 2026  
**Official Documentation:** https://docs.salla.dev/

