### 3.7 Complete twilight.json Example for Tharaa Theme

```json
{
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "theme_name": "Tharaa - Ã˜Â«Ã˜Â±Ã˜Â§Ã˜Â¡",
  "repo_url": "https://github.com/your-username/tharaa-theme",
  "support_url": "https://tharaa-theme.com/support",
  
  "settings": [
    {
      "key": "colors",
      "type": "collection",
      "label": "Ã˜Â§Ã™â€Ã˜Â£Ã™â€Ã™Ë†Ã˜Â§Ã™â€ ",
      "label_en": "Colors",
      "fields": [
        {
          "key": "primary_color",
          "type": "color",
          "label": "Ã˜Â§Ã™â€Ã™â€Ã™Ë†Ã™â€  Ã˜Â§Ã™â€Ã˜Â£Ã˜Â³Ã˜Â§Ã˜Â³Ã™Å ",
          "label_en": "Primary Color",
          "default": "#1a1a1a"
        },
